itemLabel: Milo Talbot, 7th Baron Talbot of Malahide

wikipedia_page.main: Milo John Reginald Talbot, 7th Baron Talbot of Malahide  (1 December 1912 – 14 April 1973), was an Anglo-Irish aristocrat, British diplomat, and accomplished Irish botanist and horticulturist.
